code: export var MinutesPassed=function MinutesPassed(date){var date1=new Date();var date2=new Date(date);var diffTime=date2-date1;return diffTime/(1000*60);};export var GetDateString=function GetDateString(date){var d=null;d=date?new Date(date):new Date();var month=''+(d.getMonth()+1),day=''+d.getDate(),year=d.getFullYear(),hours=d.getHours(),mins=d.getMinutes();if(month>=1&month<=9)month='0'+month.toString();if(day>=0&day<=9)day='0'+day.toString();if(hours>=0&hours<=9)hours='0'+hours.toString();if(mins>=0&mins<=9)mins='0'+mins.toString();return[year,month,day].join('-')+'T'+[hours,mins].join(':');};
